50|$|The Joint Network Node is {{a system}} {{developed}} to replace the Mobile Subscriber Equipment (MSE) for the United States Military. It provides <b>Beyond</b> <b>Line</b> <b>of</b> <b>Sight</b> (BLOS) capabilities for the Warfighter.|$|E
