50|$|Developed in {{the early}} '90's, the SMART-T {{provides}} <b>Beyond</b> LOS (<b>Line</b> <b>Of</b> <b>Sight)</b> range extensions for Division level, Brigade Level, and Battalion Level elements. The SMART-T provides protected Command and Control (C2) communications through use of EHF (Extremely High Frequency) waveforms over Military used satellite constellations.|$|R
